1625
01:05:53,018 --> 01:05:55,217
- That's why we didn't prepare.
- The MBC Best Singer Award...

1626
01:05:55,218 --> 01:05:57,217
- in 1971...
- That's right.

1627
01:05:57,218 --> 01:05:59,658
always considered the contribution to MBC.

1628
01:05:59,728 --> 01:06:01,757
I had just come from Vietnam,

1629
01:06:01,758 --> 01:06:03,897
