He wasn't included...

1659
01:07:04,958 --> 01:07:07,027
- among the top ten singers.
- Right.

1660
01:07:07,028 --> 01:07:09,088
- among the top ten singers.
- Right.

1661
01:07:10,228 --> 01:07:11,858
It's true.

1662
01:07:11,928 --> 01:07:14,597
He wasn't included among the top ten singers in MBC.

1663
01:07:14,598 --> 01:07:15,827
He was there.

1664
01:07:15,828 --> 01:07:17,568
He was listed once, but never again.

1665
01:07:17,698 --> 01:07:20,007
I remember that better.

1666
01:07:20,008 --> 01:07:22,007
I remember that from my childhood as well.

