- Right.
- That's right.

1671
01:07:31,018 --> 01:07:33,047
(Nam Jin versus Na Hoon A)

1672
01:07:33,048 --> 01:07:36,358
(The legendary rivals of the Korean pop music)

1673
01:07:37,158 --> 01:07:40,987
(Na Hoon A and Nam Jin, lifelong companions)

