(Na Hoon A and Nam Jin, lifelong rivals)

1675
01:07:44,028 --> 01:07:46,097
You had to say Nam Jin and Na Hoon A.

1676
01:07:46,098 --> 01:07:48,897
If someone said Na Hoon A and Nam Jin, it would create chaos.

1677
01:07:48,898 --> 01:07:50,337
You had to put his name first.

1678
01:07:50,338 --> 01:07:52,067
(A time when even the order of names caused a stir)

1679
01:07:52,068 --> 01:07:54,938
Have you never met Na Hoon A's fans?

1680
01:07:55,238 --> 01:07:56,637
We met.

1681
01:07:56,638 --> 01:07:58,407
They had a fight.

1682
01:07:58,408 --> 01:07:59,408
