1683
01:07:59,409 --> 01:08:01,907
Even on other TV networks,

1684
01:08:01,908 --> 01:08:04,318
they were listed as candidates.

1685
01:08:04,778 --> 01:08:07,617
One of the two had to be the top.

1686
01:08:07,618 --> 01:08:11,388
So we all waited with flowers.

1687
01:08:11,658 --> 01:08:14,727
