1688
01:08:14,728 --> 01:08:15,997
But those fans...

1689
01:08:15,998 --> 01:08:18,457
threw things and cursed us.

1690
01:08:18,458 --> 01:08:20,397
They thought they would win the award.

1691
01:08:20,398 --> 01:08:22,298
We didn't just stand by either.

1692
01:08:22,738 --> 01:08:24,767
We went there...

1693
01:08:24,768 --> 01:08:26,108
and grabbed their hair.

1694
01:08:28,168 --> 01:08:29,378
It's too much, isn't it?

1695
01:08:29,478 --> 01:08:31,478
- I mean...
- We'd fight.

1696
01:08:32,108 --> 01:08:33,877
Because of those fans,

1697
01:08:33,878 --> 01:08:35,507
we had our heyday.

1698
01:08:35,508 --> 01:08:36,617
Or else,

1699
01:08:36,618 --> 01:08:38,578
- I wouldn't have made it there.
- Right.

1700
