I wouldn't have made it.

1701
01:08:40,918 --> 01:08:45,518
A little after 2000, I was diagnosed with cancer.

1702
01:08:45,758 --> 01:08:49,528
And he sent me...

1703
01:08:51,128 --> 01:08:52,997
an envelope.

1704
01:08:52,998 --> 01:08:55,267
It wasn't the money that mattered.

1705
01:08:55,268 --> 01:08:58,237
It was the thought that he cared about me.

1706
01:08:58,238 --> 01:09:00,068
I was truly thankful...

1707
01:09:00,468 --> 01:09:03,178
and happy. I still am.

1708
01:09:03,908 --> 01:09:06,848
I was running a furniture store. One day it caught fire...

1709
01:09:08,208 --> 01:09:09,878
and everything was destroyed.

1710
01:09:09,948 --> 01:09:11,918
Every single piece of furniture was lost.

1711
01:09:13,118 --> 01:09:15,187
I couldn't work for months.

1712
01:09:15,188 --> 01:09:17,658
During that time, he helped me.

1713
01:09:17,988 --> 01:09:20,057
Thanks to him, I was able to rent a larger space,

1714
01:09:20,058 --> 01:09:21,328
and I've been running the store there ever since.

1715
01:09:21,758 --> 01:09:23,198
I'm truly grateful.

1716
01:09:23,628 --> 01:09:27,798
I tear up like this whenever I talk about it.

1717
01:09:28,268 --> 01:09:29,737
I can't express how thankful I am.

1718
01:09:29,738 --> 01:09:30,838
(I can't express how thankful I am.)

1719
01:09:31,038 --> 01:09:34,337
For 50 or 60 years,

1720
01:09:34,338 --> 01:09:38,038
they've been staying by my side like family.

1721
01:09:38,678 --> 01:09:42,878
It's a truly special bond.

1722
01:09:43,078 --> 01:09:44,778
Our lives are built on relationships,

1723
01:09:45,678 --> 01:09:48,747
