1724
01:09:48,748 --> 01:09:50,158
They really gave me a lot.

1725
01:09:50,658 --> 01:09:53,527
I wasn't able to repay them as much as I should have,

1726
01:09:53,528 --> 01:09:55,987
but I made a heartfelt promise to myself...

1727
01:09:55,988 --> 01:09:59,027
to spend the rest of my life...

1728
01:09:59,028 --> 01:10:00,067
- giving back to my fans.
- Our

